  <brief_title>Injectable Lidocaine Versus Lidocaine/Tetracaine Patch for the Incision and Drainage of Skin Abscesses</brief_title>
  <official_title>Injectable Lidocaine Provides Similar Analgesia Compared to Transdermal Lidocaine/Tetracaine Patch for the Incision and Drainage of Skin Abscesses: A Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
